download node.js-->
instal it with all permission-->
go to your code space(vs code) create a new folder for tailwind-->
open terminal( go to view-> click on terminal->)-->
open the tailwind website in your web-->
get these link and paste in the terminal with added "vite"->(npm install -D tailwindcss vite)-->
it will take some time to process-->
get the another link from the website and paste in the terminal with added "-p" ->(npx tailwindcss init -p)
new pacakages appears in the folder-->
open "tailwind.config.js" and add "content:["*"]"
open "package.json" and add 
"scripts": {
    "start": "vite"
  },"
